1. Start RBS simulation.

2. Send NM frame activating a PN in which PTM participates

Rte_UserSwitchLogic_R_RX_PwrRrClsrModeSeltn_PwrRrClsrModeSeltn_Buf

6. Stop Sending CAN signal SrlDat2_Prtctd_PDU ($27A)

8. Read Rte_UserSwitchLogic_R_RX_PwrRrClsrModeSeltn_PwrRrClsrModeSeltn_Buf

7. Check fault status 
DTC_U014000 is set 

8. Rte_UserSwitchLogic_R_RX_PwrRrClsrModeSeltn_PwrRrClsrModeSeltn_Buf is equal to last known position 

9. Rte_CanWrapper_RPort_SrlDat2_Prtctd_LcFA_LcFA_Buf is equal to 1
c_Observed_Result:
7. Check fault status 
DTC_U014000 is set 

8. Rte_UserSwitchLogic_R_RX_PwrRrClsrModeSeltn_PwrRrClsrModeSeltn_Buf is equal to last known position 

9. Rte_CanWrapper_RPort_SrlDat2_Prtctd_LcFA_LcFA_Buf is equal to 1
